"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-24-olympics-football-match-chaos-every-fan-kicked-stadium-21291472\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"There was chaos on the first day of football action at the Paris Olympicsbetween Argentina and Moroccowith the match halted by a furious pitch invasion - eventually concluding in an empty stadium after a two-hour delay.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.035079969429278e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 81, \"end\": 90, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.641433507233016e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morocco looked to be on course to a famous win at Stade Geoffroy-Guichard in St-Etienne, leading Argentina 2-1 as the game headed towards its conclusion.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999832584764, \"rank\": 1.4344795580399065e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the 16th minute of added time, Boca Juniors midfielder Cristian Medina headed home after the ball had twice come back off the crossbar.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boca_Juniors\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8565110237011215e-25, \"text\": \"Boca Juniors\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boca_Juniors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boca_Juniors\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cristian Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristian_Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It sparked a furious reaction from Morocco supporters who made their way onto the pitch to throw bottles and flares.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999832584764, \"rank\": 1.4344795580399065e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Images showed Argentina players flinching when what appeared to be a fire cracker was thrown in the direction of their bench.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.641433507233016e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match official blew his whistle but not for full-time, with the game suspended while the chaos was cleared.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The match was officially deemed to have been 'interrupted' by Paris 2024's official website.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999982894678, \"rank\": 1.7104424788010512e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over an hour later, it was decided the match would officially resume for the final three minutes, with supporters cleared from the stands.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro's Head of Sport James Goldman delivers punchy analysis, transfer talk and his take on the week's biggest stories direct to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Goldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q28389\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up here, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And in another incredible development, Medina's would-be equaliser was wiped out by the video assistant referee, judging the Argentina star to have been in an offside position.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6093506557727949e-19, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.641433507233016e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The goal that sparked the pitch invasion was promptly overturned with Morocco holding on for the final minutes to seal a famous win.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999832584764, \"rank\": 1.4344795580399065e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soufiane Rahimi had put Morocco ahead in the final seconds of the first half and Rahimi struck again from the penalty spot in the 49th minute.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soufiane_Rahimi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Soufiane Rahimi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soufiane_Rahimi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soufiane_Rahimi\"}, {\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999832584764, \"rank\": 1.4344795580399065e-08, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Giuliano Simeone pulled one back for Javier Mascherano's side in the 68th minute before Medina struck deep into injury time